Ubuntu & Debian : 
sudo apt install libpcap0.8 libpcap0.8-dev libncurses5 libncurses5-dev
sudo apt install iftop
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Atau jika kalian pengguna CentOS, iftop tersedia di repository EPEL.
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
CentOS : 
yum  -y install libpcap libpcap-devel ncurses ncurses-devel
yum install epel-release
yum install  iftop
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
cd iftop-0.17
./configure
make
make install
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Cara menggunakan iftop juga cukup mudah. Untuk penggunaaan dasar bisa gunakan perintah:
sudo iftop
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Dengan iftop kalian bisa memantau interface tertentu misal memantau interface WiFi saja maka perintahnya:
sudo iftop -i wlan0
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
